  "bodyTextHead": "For you\nNew thread\nSearch\nMessages\nActivity\nProfile\nInsights\nSaved\nFeeds\nEdit\nFollowing\nGhost posts\nMore\nFor you\nFollowing\nGhost posts\nWhat's new?\nPost\nzac_yutai\nClaudeCode\n1h\n原來用Fable5的好處是\nCode 2.5小時，可以強迫自己改做其他工作2.5小時\nTranslate\n2\nbsunter\nAI Threads\n5h\nHit my claude limits in 13 minutes with one prompt on the $100 plan.\n5\n3\nse_ranking\n7h\nCan AI content actually be good?\n6\n17\nclarice.felicia\nLove Island USA\n2h\nWhy can’t I vote????\n@loveislandusa\n it’s been hours and I’m still getting error messages\n56\n11\n3\nboris_cherny\n9h\nFable 5 is the biggest step up I’ve felt in our models since Opus 4.5 back in November. After 4.5 came out I uninstalled my IDE when I realized that I’d been doing 100% of my coding in a terminal for a few weeks. With Fable, it’s felt like Claude has stepped up from being a coding agent to a thought and design partner in building the product. Fable has judgement, taste, and dimensionality in a way that previous models didn’t, leading me to trust it more with the most complex work.\n1\n/\n3\n1K\n96\n42\n43\ngorgo.inanna\nLove Island USA\n4h\nDid you MFs crash the app?!? Why can’t I vote 😡😡😡\n8\nkasetheace\n17h\nWho’s the best with Claude code / Claude co work? Looking for someo",
